 Create a Wallet - download metamask or your wallet of choice from the app store or google play store for free. Desktopusers, download the google chrome extension by going to metamask.io.

 Get Some BNB - have BNB in your wallet to switch to $BABYPEPE. If you don’t have any BNB, you can buy directly on metamask, transfer from another wallet, or buy on another exchange and send it to your wallet.

 Go to PancakeSWap - connect to Pancakeswap. Paste the $BABYPEPE token address into PancakeSwap, select BABYPEPE, and confirm. When Metamask prompts you for a wallet signature, sign.

 Switch BNB for $BABYPEPE - switch ETH for $BABYPEPE. We have ZERO taxes so you don’t need to worry about buying with a specific slippage, although you may need to use slippage during times of market volatility.

 LOW Taxes, No Bullshit. It’s that simple. - 56% of the tokens were sent to the liquidity pool, LP tokens were lock 1 year, and contract is renounced. The remaining 11% of the supply is being held in a multi-sig wallet only to be used as tokens for future centralized exchange listings, bridges, and liquidity pools.
